Hypnosis
A heart will cry without any technical reasons.
I’m too drunk at night, we can’t assort the keys.
And nobody is guilty, and we are sounding for ourselves.
Enclose me in embrace and beat in my chest.
 
The world touched by cold palms has holes of unidentified depth everywhere.(2x)
 
Let me gather myself. What do you mean: I can’t do the opposite.
Rhytms of pulsations, I’m flourishing for you.
A dream, waking up then. Rhytms of pulsations.
 
We can only decide how much we breath together.
We’re on razor’s edge, souls are too „naked”.
We can only decide how much we breath together.
We’re on razor’s edge, souls are too „naked”.
 
Forever, to perpetuity(4x)
 
Let me gather myself. What do you mean: I can’t do the opposite.
Rhytms of pulsations, I’m flourishing for you.
